title: Hinokio Inter Galactic Love (2005)
description:
Fantastic film about a young, shy boy named Satoru who attends school through a remote controlled robot. Entertaining for both children and adults, "Hinokio" presents a realistic yet sci-fi description of the friendships and emotions of childhood with stunning visual effects!

Director: Takahiko Akiyama
